msgid "Subscriptions saved."
msgstr "Subskripsi disimpan"

msgid "Update"
msgstr "Pembaruan"

msgid "Attempting to update addressbook from subscription sources..."
msgstr "Mencoba memperbarui buku alamat dari sumber langganan..."

msgid "Cannot update subscriptions: HTTP proxy is not running!"
msgstr "Tidak dapat memperbarui langganan: Proksi HTTP tidak berjalan!"

msgid "Subscriptions reloaded."
msgstr "Subskripsi dimuat ulang"

msgid "If SusiDNS is configured to publish your Router address book, the entries will appear in your Published address book and saved to a hosts.txt file for sharing."
msgstr "Jika DNS diatur untuk mempublikasikan buku alamat router Anda, daftarnya akan muncul di buku alamat yang dipublikasikan dan disimpan ke file hosts.txt supaya dapat disebarkan."

msgid "Published Addressbook"
msgstr "Addressbook Terpublikasi"

msgid "To configure SusiDNS to push your Router address book to your Published address book, set 'should_publish=true' on the configuration page."
msgstr "Supaya DNS mendorong addressbook router Anda ke addressbook terpublikasi, ubah menjadi 'should_publish=true' di halaman pengaturan atau configuration page."

msgid "All hosts derived from subscriptions will appear in this address book, in addition to any you manually add here or to your Master address book."
msgstr "Semua host yang diambil dari subscription atau langganan akan muncul di address book, termasuk yang Anda tambahkan secara manual atau dari address book master."

msgid "Router Addressbook"
msgstr "Addressbook Router"

msgid "Hosts you manually add here will never be published. You can also add aliases to hosts in other address books here."
msgstr "Host yang ditambahkan secara manual di sini tidak akan pernah dipublikasikan. Di sini Anda juga dapat menambahkan alias kepada host di address book lain."

msgid "Private Addressbook"
msgstr "Addressbook Privat"

msgid "Local Records"
msgstr "Catatan Lokal"

msgid "I2P applications (including the HTTP proxy) use the hosts in your local address books to resolve .i2p hostnames."
msgstr "Aplikasi I2P (termasuk proxy HTTP) menggunakan nama host di addressbook lokal Anda untuk menemukan alamat .2p."

msgid "Additional subscriptions can be found in the FAQ section of the Router help page."
msgstr "Subskripsi atau langganan tambahan dapat ditemukan di bagian FAQ di halaman bantuan Router."

msgid "Subscriptions"
msgstr "Subskripsi"

msgid "Hosts sourced from your subscriptions are added to your Router address book, and are automatically synced (by default every 12 hours)."
msgstr "Host yang berasal dari subskripsi Anda ditambahkan ke addressbook router dan secara otomatis disinkronisasi (standarnya setiap 12 jam)."

msgid "Configure Subscriptions"
msgstr "Pengaturan Langganan"

msgid "If you manually add hosts here, they will be included your Published address book (if configured)."
msgstr "Jika Anda menambahkan host secara manual ke sini, host akan dimasukkan ke dalam addressbook terpublikasi (jika ini diatur demikian)."

msgid "Master Addressbook"
msgstr "Addressbook Master"

msgid "Searchable by"
msgstr "Dapat dicari oleh"

msgid "I2P applications"
msgstr "Aplikasi I2P"

msgid "The Master, Router and Private address books collectively serve as the DNS authority for I2P applications."
msgstr "Addressbook Master, Router, dan Privat secara bersamaan berfungsi sebagai DNS untuk aplikasi I2P."

msgid "Optional,"
msgstr "Pilihan tambahan,"

msgid "for websites"
msgstr "untuk situs web"

msgid "If you configure SusiDNS to publish your Router address book, it will export a hosts.txt file containing all the hosts (by default to the root of your eepsite)."
msgstr "Jika Anda mengatur DNS untuk mempublikasikan addressbook router Anda, DNS akan mengekspor file host.txt yang berisi semua host (secara default ke folder root di eepsite Anda)."

msgid "Addresses manually added to your Master address book will merge with your Router address book."
msgstr "Addressbook yang ditambahkan secara manual ke addressbook master akan bergabung ke dalam addressbook router."

msgid "Hosts you receive from your subscriptions will merge with your Router address book."
msgstr "Host yang Anda dapatkan dari langganan akan bergabung dengan addressbook router."
